<h1>
Participate
</h1>
<p class='participate-join'>
<span class='highlight'>
Join by hosting your own #ScienceHack!
</span>
</p>
<div class='participate-how-left'>
<img alt="Violacein-factory-2" class="participate-how-logo" src="//synbiotaalpha.s3.amazonaws.com/beta/assets/sciencehack_phase2/images/violacein-factory-2-3c1e22859b587cee058628e523ab5db4.png" />
<p class='participate-how-hint'>
The Violacein Factory Kit simplifies metabolic engineering through the use of standardized Genomikon DNA parts that speed up the discovery process
</p>
</div>
<div class='participate-how-body'>
<h2>How?</h2>
<ol class='circled-list-items'>
<li>Form a team of up to 15 people with at least one scientist.</li>
<li>Order a #ScienceHack Violacein Factory Kit.</li>
<li>Checkout the other Violacein Factories to gain insight.</li>
<li>Start hacking!</li>
</ol>
